      "Text": "Security update for perl-DBI",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for perl-DBI fixes the following issues\n\n- CVE-2026-9698: DBI versions before 1.648 for Perl saved errors in a limited-sized buffer (bsc#1267957).\n- CVE-2026-10879: SQL statements with more than 9 binders can cause an heap overflow (bsc#1267849).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
